      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANCY DEVERE (2) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 6th and beaten 16 lengths at Sandown (30.30). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Can make amends. IN A BIT (4) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing eighth (30.38) at Sandown last time. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. KNURLING (1) was in the minors two back (30.64) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 7th. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has ability and can atone. RIPPED PAIGE (8) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
